message.text:
Heads up, Tamaraws!
Starting Monday, September 22, FEU will strictly implement the Uniform Policy for all students — old, new, and returning. 
✅ Wear your prescribed school attire
✅ Always bring and wear your FEU ID
📍New students can claim their IDs at the Visitors Lounge, Engineering Building (6:00 AM–7:00 PM)

#TatakTamaraw #FEUCoreValues #FEUUniformPolicy

message.text:
Heads up, Tamaraws!
Starting Monday, September 22, FEU will strictly implement the Uniform Policy for all students — old, new, and returning. 
✅ Wear your prescribed school attire
✅ Always bring and wear your FEU ID
📍New students can claim their IDs at the Visitors Lounge, Engineering Building (6:00 AM–7:00 PM)

#TatakTamaraw #FEUCoreValues #FEUUniformPolicy

#TatakTamaraw #FEUCoreValues #FEUUniformPolicy

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

Caption by: Ysha Patapat
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#PATAPHFEU
#WTD2025

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Host: Ace Chezter Sibaro
Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
Scriptwriter: Ronn Jasper Repulda and Ace Chezter Sibaro
Videographer: MJ Astilla and Nicole Villa
Editor: Nicole Villa
Caption: Ahzel Uy
Music: Eraserheads - Ligaya

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Host: Ace Chezter Sibaro
Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
Scriptwriter: Ronn Jasper Repulda and Ace Chezter Sibaro
Videographer: MJ Astilla and Nicole Villa
Editor: Nicole Villa
Caption: Ahzel Uy
Music: Eraserheads - Ligaya

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno

Editor: Nicole Villa

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
🎥 Bawat Kanto, Bagong Simula: Maligayang Pagdating sa Maynila! 🎬

Sa pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025, muling nabuo ang mga alaala ng pagkakaisa, kasiyahan, at pakikipagkaibigan. Isa itong paglalakbay na nagbukas ng panibagong kuwento para sa mga Tamaraw na nagnanais tuklasin ang mundo ng pagseserbisyo kasama ang IABF Student Council.

Balikan natin ang mga kaganapan at pakulo na naging bahagi ng makulay na selebrasyon na ito—at hayaan nating muling mabuhay ang kwento sa pamamagitan ng bidyong ito. ✨

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Director: RB Benito and Heart Nepomuceno
